Class Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • Event
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Event>

    public class Event
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Event>
    The Event class is used to represent an event at the World Sports Championship. The class holds the name of the event along with the number of tickets.
